You know, it's not easy
living in the suburbs

I have to care for my family,
our pets, our lawn and more

Not to mention having to look
perfect every...single...day

Though it's nice when the kids
head to school and I can relax

picking up a good book or even
pushing it inside the bookshelf

to re-enter my secret world
where I can keep all safe

but I have to be prepared, always
having the right tools available

because really, I'm not just
Mom...I'm SUPER Mom!!!
